This creates a comprehensive, reusable setting-card web component featuring:
Input Types Supported:
Toggle: Animated switch with keyboard accessibility
Slider: Numeric range with live value display and unit suffixes
Select: Dropdown with JSON-defined options
Text/Number: Standard inputs with debounced change events
Color: Native color picker
Keybind: Interactive keyboard shortcut recorder (supports modifiers)
File: File picker with filename display
Button: Action trigger
Visual Variants:
default: Standard card with full description
compact: Icon + label only, description hidden
prominent: Elevated background for important settings
danger: Red accent for destructive actions
Special Features:
Badges: Beta, Premium, and "Requires Restart" indicators
Loading State: Overlay spinner for async operations
Disabled State: Visual dimming with interaction blocking
Sharingan Theme Integration: CSS custom properties for EMS visual effects
Accessibility: ARIA labels, keyboard navigation, focus management
Technical Highlights:
Shadow DOM encapsulation with CSS custom properties for theming
Debounced input handling for performance
Programmatic API (get/set value, loading, disabled states)
Custom events for parent component communication
Responsive design with CSS Grid/Flexbox